<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
Invitation To Comment
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Interested parties are invited to provide comments on the draft SEIS. DOE will consider written and oral comments
equally when preparing the final SEIS. Written comments should be sent to Dr. K.L. Hooker at the address given above.
To be considered in the final SEIS, written comments should be postmarked by October 11, 1994; comments postmarked
after that date will be considered to the extent practicable.
